        <updateDate>2021-08-23T16:06:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Secure United States Bases Act</b></p>This bill revises requirements related to U.S.-based foreign military training programs. <p>Specifically, the bill</p> <ul> <li>creates a visa category for certain aliens who have been accepted into a U.S.-based military training program;</li> <li>adds application, vetting, and monitoring requirements for foreign military trainees; and</li> <li>requires the Department of Defense to develop a method for classifying the relative risk, by country, of accepting foreign personnel into U.S. military training programs.</li></ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
